column5: Furnished private bedroom with TV, Free Wi-Fi, Closet, you will have your own Bathroom/Shower just 4 feet away from the bedroom.  With Access to Kitchen, Laundry, Living Room, Backyard, & Bikes.  The Room is in a 4 bedroom home built in 2004, Quite & Safe neighborhood. Very close to Frisco! There's Toyota Stadium for concerts and soccer, Dallas Cowboys Headquarters, Frisco RoughRiders Baseball Stadium, and Dr Pepper StarCenter to watch hockey nearby.
